Key Security MeasuresAuthentication: Verifies users with OAuth/JWT or encrypted passwords. Ensures only valid users access the platform.
Authorization: Restricts actions by role (host/guest) via RBAC. Prevents unauthorized access to features.
Rate Limiting: Caps API requests to block abuse. Maintains system performance.

Why Security is CrucialUser Data: Authentication/authorization protect sensitive info, ensuring privacy.
Payments: Encryption prevents fraud, securing transactions.
Booking System: Rate limiting/authorization ensure fair, reliable bookings.
Property Management: Authorization prevents unauthorized listing changes.

